@@gPUGILIST@@W

Pugilists are close-quarters specialists who trust stamina, timing, and body
control over steel. They outlast opponents, then punish every opening.

@@gPassive class abilities@@W
  * @@wPugilist technique scaling@@W: palmstrike/pummel/aurabolt gain
    @@w+0.5% damage per Pugilist level@@W.
  * @@wCounter@@W (unlocked at mortal level 20): enables counterattacks when
    enemies miss and your counter chance succeeds.

@@gUnique Pugilist mechanics@@W
  * Prime mortal attribute is @@wConstitution@@W.
  * Builds toward reactive melee defense through counterplay and sustained
    unarmed pressure.

@@gPugilist reincarnation bonuses@@W
  * Every @@w2 Pugilist reincarnations@@W (rounded up) increases max
    @@wConstitution@@W by 1.
  * At @@w1+ Pugilist reincarnation@@W, @@wCounter@@W is permanently unlocked
    for all future class paths.

